BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: The Mindful Stream
UID:event_313953905@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260410T030800Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260414T213000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260414T223000
SUMMARY:Awakening Awareness: Embracing This Moment
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\nFeel free to join as we get still and prac
 tise presence within this moment. We will discuss and observe the obstacle
 s that\, seemingly\, block us from being present and bring awareness to ou
 r unconsciousness in a safe\, inclusive and affirming way.\n\nSessions are
  suitable for newcomers\, those experienced in Tolle's teaching and anyone
  wishing to remain completely anonymous.\n\nSee you there!\n\nPlease be aw
 are that sessions will close if no members have joined after 10 minutes.\n
 \nEmrys has been passionate about mindfulness since 2010 and since 2021 he
  has been organising free\, weekly online meditation groups. For more info
 rmation on his free Work of Byron Katie online mediation group\, visit [th
 is Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/themindfulstream/events/313953905/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260326T015753Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260326T015753Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: The Mindful Stream
UID:event_313974215@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260410T030800Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260415T213000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260415T223000
SUMMARY:Beginners in The Work of Byron Katie: Newcomers Welcome
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream\nA free Zoom meditation session designed wi
 th newcomers in mind. Sessions will include at least one hour of facilitat
 ion (meditation) and there is room for questions and answers throughout. I
 f you're curious about The Work\, you're invited to join!\n\nSee you there
 !\n\nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no members have joined af
 ter 10 minutes.\n\n**To book a free introductory private session with Emry
 s\, [click here](https://calendly.com/mindfulnesswithemrys/onehoursession)
 [.](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)**\n\nEmrys also organises
  a free Work of Byron Katie Meetup group. Visit: [https://www.meetup.com/t
 hework-runsfree](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/)\n\n*Find out mo
 re about Emrys [here](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)[.](http
 ://linktr.ee/theworkrunsfree)*\n\nTo best prepare for each session\, compl
 ete a *Judge Your Neighbour* worksheet free at [https://thework.com/part-t
 hree/](https://thework.com/part-three/) or visit [http://www.thework.com](
 http://www.thework.com)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/themindfulstream/events/313974215/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260327T024824Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260327T024824Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
